1.0.name: wordpress/wp-alp
1.0.description:
Simple apache log parser for Wordpress. Monitor site usage by ip-address. Adds a dashboard graph widget displaying the daily bandwidth usage.

If you have installed the WP-IP2Nation-Installer the stats will automatically include an extra "country" table column.

Download WP-IP2Nation-Installer here: http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wp-ip2nation-installer/
